{"id": 6187, "title": "Ticket #6187: Improve collector speed by not param'ing on every attribute", "description": "<blockquote>\nWhen the collector sends ads back to a client in response to a query, every attribute of every ad is checked to see if it looks like an IP address, and if so, if it needs to be re-written because of TCP_FORWARDING_HOST or other reasons.  The code param's to make this decision, which is slow.  We need to cache this param in a condor_reconfig aware way.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2017-Apr-17 17:31:58 by tim:</em> <br/>\n\n<strong>DOC REVIEW:</strong> OK</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2017-Mar-13 16:52</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/5280cc3f222f4c4238b51a917ff07738a5d54c77\">[50309]</a></span>: Document <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=6187\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6187'); return false;\" title=\"Improve collector speed by not param'ing on every attribute\">#6187</a></span>  (By Greg Thain )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2017-Mar-13 16:19</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/36fee680a8af5f98b942d7748e5ed7beb4b4c4fa\">[50308]</a></span>: Cache param'ing of SHARED_PORT_ADDRESS_REWRITING to speed collector <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=6187\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6187'); return false;\" tit